➜凤萍（香港）：急雨
http://www.sohu.com/a/419300061_100115135	37247
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200918/6bc6fe6313204cccb5fd5ebb78aee0a3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>急雨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/凤萍</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">刚刚还见血红的晚霞描绘着秋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">此刻的香江随时给秋一阵酸雨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">收割夕阳的余晖</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">船舶在大海里舞动</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人们在路灯下，街道上挣扎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>天空飘下狂风暴雨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>淋湿了大地上行走的脚印</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>掰开尘土里隐藏的秘密</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>毫不客气，一丝一毫也不放弃</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">此刻的傍晚似乎睡醒后的秋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">斑驳光影是岁月赐予的温柔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在一颗坚强的心上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">陪伴着日渐苍老松弛的皮囊</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">与大地相伴，与世界对话</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2020.09.17</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200918/d645ea022dbe40b6a0ed68d73abc57e8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
