➜广东诗人辉哥：秋思
http://www.sohu.com/a/419342455_100115135	54602
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200918/4ffc4e266a0a4ac992811e1d15a84e26.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>秋思（改）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/辉哥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">八月清风起，秋声又一程；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">碧池知水润，黄叶见枝轻；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">野草朝霜湿，园花夕照明；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相思无语处，独坐伴风声。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200918/dada6ed5469d4109824ebdb41a4ba867.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>围炉诗情辉哥，来自广东梅县客家，自小在客家农村长大，对客家文化情有独钟。喜爱古诗词，涂鸦作品多用于自耍。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200918/18d1deaedd2f4c7d926e433044e21211.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
